-NMK2K7BHiYNcHPJT-Fn.name: Apollo
-NMK2K7BHiYNcHPJT-Fn.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this distinctive Lab mix comes from the Florida Little Dog rescue group in St. Cloud, Florida. Silly Apollo may be the team comedian, but this little pup knows when to get down to business! One thing’s for sure, when Apollo is in the spotlight, anything can happen!

-NMK2K7GXVWHIpxdDB-q.name: Bacon
-NMK2K7GXVWHIpxdDB-q.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this Terrier comes from the Vintage Pet Rescue in Foster, Rhode Island. It's obvious this happy-go-lucky puppy doesn't let his disability hold him back. Joey’s new wheels let him chase his need for speed and beat the competition! Joey is proof you can’t keep a good pup down.

-NMK2K7I2991Q7btokHp.name: Betty
-NMK2K7I2991Q7btokHp.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this Terrier comes from NAGI Foundation in Phoenix, Arizona. Shy Betty is a world class snuggler, but don't let this introvert fool you. She is ready to use her talents for touchdowns. This pup is testing her limits, coming off the sidelines and heading to the goal line.

-NMK2K7LvqC7dH8hHdu0.name: Bleu
-NMK2K7LvqC7dH8hHdu0.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this American Staffordshire Terrier/ American Foxhound mix is from the Furever I Love Atlanta shelter in Atlanta, Georgia. A curious pup with a nose for clues, Bleu is bringing his smarts, heart and bark out to the field! He is NOT afraid to go head to head… Color yourself surprised if you count out Bleu!

-NMK2K7PQoQijlFSzZli.name: Butter Bean
-NMK2K7PQoQijlFSzZli.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this pup comes from Buddy’s Second Chance Rescue in Buffalo, New York. This pupper is ready to go pro and show these doggies what he’s made of! He is a friend to canines big and small, loves to paddle in the water bowl, and is one of the most valuable pups to have on the team.

-NMK2K7SCznw6LmWxKkx.name: Chickpea
-NMK2K7SCznw6LmWxKkx.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this pup comes from the Humane Society of Dominica in Roseau, Dominica. She’s traveled a long way, and boy, she came to PLAY! Chickpea may be a sweetie, but she’s also quite the contender! If she doesn’t get distracted by cuddles, there’s no telling what this hound can do!

-NMK2K7VHQma1dwdS2AA.name: Clover
-NMK2K7VHQma1dwdS2AA.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this feisty pup comes from IndyHumane in Indianapolis, Indiana. She’s been dealt some hardships, but Clover has too big a heart to count her out! Nothing stops this gal! This tenacious pup is all pupped up and ready to run with the big dogs.

-NMK2K7Y62IdsRacptNo.name: Daisy
-NMK2K7Y62IdsRacptNo.description: As a member of Team Ruff, this gal comes from Bosley’s Place in Smyrna, Georgia. Petite puppy Daisy may be the smallest player in the game, but she's sure to give the big pups the challenge of their lives. Can this shy, little pup find her footing and make a big play on game day? Or, make a friend? Either way, Daisy is a winner!

-NMK2K7_OW0K4keArejT.name: Davinci
-NMK2K7_OW0K4keArejT.description: As a member of Team Fluff, this pup comes from the Florida Little Dog Rescue in St. Cloud, Florida. A playful little pup with big dog energy, Davinci is sure to score! And he has a touchdown dance ready when that happens. He is here to take a chomp out of the competition! And a lick too.
